description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a highly motivated, adaptable and conscientious Pharmacy Assistant Technical Officer to help support the development of our Pharmacy service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The posts will be based at Glangwili General Hospital, which is a busy hospital with approximately 420 beds. The specialties provided here include acute medical and surgical, HDU and ICU, orthopaedics and paediatrics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role of the successful candidate will include dispensing in-patient, out-patient and discharge supplies. You will help develop the services to wards and departments as well as providing a stock management service to these areas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants are also expected to partake in a Saturday and Bank Holiday rota within the main dispensary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; English and/or Welsh speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interviews will be held on 17.11.20&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
